short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A free Chrome extension adding Maps to the Suffolk County Library Catalog.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
While using search.livebrary.com or discover.livebrary.com, links appear within search results providing map functionality.  Click "Map Libraries!" to see geographic maps.  Click "Locate Me!" to see shelf maps (available at participating libraries).  

Contact catalogmaps631@gmail.com with any questions or visit catalogmaps631.com for more info.
